Display instructions for manual USB setup of XBOX360 controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c usb -t XBOX360 | more
Display instructions for manual bluetooth setup of XBOX360 controller:confctrl_ph.sh -p help -c bluetooth -t XBOX360 | more
Setup bluetooth XBOX360 controllers:confctrl_ph.sh -p prompt -t XBOX360
Go to Controller Status:ph_show_menu StatusManagement_Controllers
Go to Controllers:ph_show_menu Controllers
Go to Main:ph_show_menu Main
Open a shell (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):echo;cd;/bin/bash
Quit:break
Return to previous screen:return
